com.percussion.cms
Interface IPSConstants

public interface IPSConstants

This file contains various constants that are used across 2 or more editors. It serves as a registry. This includes such things as:

  • The names of xml document elements and attributes
  • The names of table columns for system tables
  • The names of system fields

NO_CORRESPONDING_REVISION_VALUE

static final int NO_CORRESPONDING_REVISION_VALUE
Revision value used when there is no corresponding actual revision. Used for the edit revison of a content item that is not checked out, or for the tip revision before it is given a meaninful value.

INVALID_WORKFLOW_ID

static final int INVALID_WORKFLOW_ID
Workflow id used when there is no workflow id exist for an content item. For example, if the object is not workflowable, its workflow id should be this value.

DEFAULT_VIEW_NAME

static final String DEFAULT_VIEW_NAME
The name of the default view to use if one has not been specified. Currently this is the sys_Default view. This is the main content editor view, includes all fields, and is linked to a stylesheet through the system def that displays the full CE UI.

static final String AUTHTYPE_PREFIX

Constant Field Values

SKIP_FIELD_VISIBILITY_RULES

static final String SKIP_FIELD_VISIBILITY_RULES
Name of the request private object to use to disable field visibility rules processing by the content editor. If value is a Boolean object with a true value, visibility rules will be disabled, otherwise it has no effect.
